          <div class="promise"><div class="promise-ico">✓</div><div class="promise-txt"><b>Custom design &amp; imagery</b><span>Senior web designer applies your brand with tailored visuals on every page</span></div></div>
          <div class="promise"><div class="promise-ico">✓</div><div class="promise-txt"><b>Responsive, standards-compliant build</b><span>Mobile-first, W3C-valid markup, WCAG 2.2 AA accessible</span></div></div>
          <div class="promise"><div class="promise-ico">✓</div><div class="promise-txt"><b>SEO &amp; LLM findability</b><span>Meta tags, sitemap, schema.org data, llms.txt &amp; clean semantics</span></div></div>
          <div class="promise"><div class="promise-ico">✓</div><div class="promise-txt if-import" style="display:none;"><b>Content rewritten &amp; migrated</b><span>Senior content strategist rewrites your pages for the new design</span></div><div class="promise-txt if-blank" style="display:none;"><b>Content written from best practices</b><span>Senior content strategist writes each page around your offers &amp; main goal</span></div></div>
          <div class="promise"><div class="promise-ico">✓</div><div class="promise-txt"><b>Brand saved to Settings</b><span>Your full brand system is stored under Settings → Brand Guidelines, editable anytime</span></div></div>
